23350.title: Extraordinary with Fareed Zakaria
23350.description: Billy Joel has sold more than 150 million records and received the Gershwin Prize for Popular Song from The Library of Congress. From his home in southern Florida, Zakaria and Joel talk the inspiration behind Joel's megahits, and more.
